'''亞歷珊卓·阿萨诺芙娜·艾爾巴金'''（{{lang-ru|Алекса́ндра Аса́новна Элбакя́н}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://runet-id.com/103103/|title=Элбакян Александра Асановна / RUNET-ID|website=runet-id.com|access-date=2017-01-07|archive-date=2017-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807193030/https://runet-id.com/103103/|dead-url=no}}</ref>；{{bd|1988年|11月6日}}）是一位[[哈萨克斯坦|哈萨克斯坦]]籍研究生、<ref>{{cite news|last1=Rosenwald|first1=Michael S.|title=This student put 50 million stolen research articles online. And they’re free.|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/this-student-put-50-million-stolen-research-articles-online-and-theyre-free/2016/03/30/7714ffb4-eaf7-11e5-b0fd-073d5930a7b7_story.html?tid=sm_fb|work=[[华盛顿邮报|Washington Post]]|date=2016-03-30|accessdate=2017-01-25|archive-date=2017-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170920135645/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/this-student-put-50-million-stolen-research-articles-online-and-theyre-free/2016/03/30/7714ffb4-eaf7-11e5-b0fd-073d5930a7b7_story.html?tid=sm_fb|dead-url=no}}</ref> 計算機程序員以及[[Sci-Hub|Sci-Hub]]的創建者。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://openaccess.unt.edu/symposium/2016/info/transcript-and-translation-sci-hub-presentation |publisher=[[北德克薩斯大學|University of North Texas]] |title=Transcript and translation of Sci-Hub presentation |access-date=2017-01-01 |archive-date=2021-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213002435/https://openaccess.unt.edu/symposium/2016/info/transcript-and-translation-sci-hub-presentation |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Dylla|first=H. Frederick|date=2016-03-21|title=No need for researchers to break the law to access scientific publications|url=http://scitation.aip.org/content/aip/magazine/physicstoday/news/10.1063/PT.5.2031|journal=Physics Today|doi=10.1063/PT.5.2031|issn=0031-9228|access-date=2017-01-25|archive-date=2016-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160728230629/http://scitation.aip.org/content/aip/magazine/physicstoday/news/10.1063/PT.5.2031|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[自然_(期刊)|自然期刊]]将她列为2016年度十大科学人物之一。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.nature.com/news/nature-s-10-1.21157#/elbakyan|title=Nature’s 10 Ten people who mattered this year.|date=2016-03-12|journal=SpringerNature|doi=10.1038/540507a|access-date=2016-03-28|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925041030/https://www.nature.com/news/nature-s-10-1.21157#/elbakyan|dead-url=no}}</ref>其事迹曾被用来与[[亚伦·斯沃茨|亚伦·斯沃茨]]相比较。<ref>{{Cite web |first=David |last=Kravets |url=https://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2016/04/a-spiritual-successor-to-aaron-swartz-is-angering-publishers-all-over-again/ |title=A spiritual successor to Aaron Swartz is angering publishers all over again |website=Ars Technica |publisher=Condé Nast |date=2016-04-03 |access-date=2016-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170111180537/http://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2016/04/a-spiritual-successor-to-aaron-swartz-is-angering-publishers-all-over-again/ |archive-date=2017-01-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

==生平==
艾爾巴金于1988年11月6日上午10時35分生于[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]的[[阿拉木圖|阿拉木圖]]<ref name="VK">{{cite web|url=https://vk.com/alexandra.elbakyan|title=Alexandra Elbakyan|website=Vk.com|language=ru|accessdate=2016-10-06|archive-date=2016-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507232355/http://vk.com/alexandra.elbakyan|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ladn.eu/reflexion/articles-parus-dans-ladn-revue/alexandra-elbakyan-la-pirate-scientifique/ |title=Alexandra Elbakyan: la pirate scientifique |year=2016 |language=fr |author={{tsl|en|Coralie Trinh Thi||Coralie Trinh Thi}} |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170111182330/http://www.ladn.eu/reflexion/articles-parus-dans-ladn-revue/alexandra-elbakyan-la-pirate-scientifique/ |archive-date=2017-01-11 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2017-08-07 }}</ref>，並由她單親母親撫養長大。用她自己的話來說，她同時具有亚美尼亚、斯拉夫和亚洲血统<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/ringo_ring/status/700626318124134400|title=Alexandra Elbakyan|website=Twitter.com|date=2016-02-19|accessdate=2016-10-06|archive-date=2016-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401033114/https://twitter.com/ringo_ring/status/700626318124134400|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

從她孩提起，她就對科學、生物學和進化論很感興趣了<ref name="автоссылка1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2016/04/frustrated-science-student-behind-sci-hub|title=The frustrated science student behind Sci-Hub|author=John Bohannon Apr. 28, 2016, 2:00 Pm|date=2016-04-26|publisher=Science {{!}} AAAS|lang=en|accessdate=2019-02-27|archive-date=2017-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170718002509/http://www.sciencemag.org/news/2016/04/alexandra-elbakyan-founded-sci-hub-thwart-journal-paywalls|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她在她網志上有其詳細個人傳記。

她12歲開始編程，學會了用[[HTML|HTML]]製作網頁，後來更會用[[PHP|PHP]]、[[Delphi|Delphi]]和[[匯編語言|匯編語言]]編寫了。

她隨後在[[阿斯塔納|阿斯塔納]]完成了大学学业。在2009年她获得了{{le|哈萨克国立科技大学|Kazakh National Technical University}}的[[计算机科学|计算机科学]][[理學士|理學士]]学位，专业为[[信息安全|信息安全]]<ref>{{cite news |page=22 |url=http://doc.utwente.nl/69553/1/bacteriahunt_e09project5.pdf |publisher=[[特文特大学|University of Twente]] |title=Bacteria Hunt:A multimodal, multiparadigm BCI game |accessdate=2017-08-07 |archive-date=2016-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604075940/http://doc.utwente.nl/69553/1/bacteriahunt_e09project5.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在此之间她成为一名[[黑客_(计算机安全)|黑客]]。

2009年大學畢業後，她移居莫斯科，並從事信息安全工作。<ref name="автоссылка1" />

其後后于2010年到德国[[弗莱堡大学|弗莱堡大学]]参与一项关于[[脑机接口|脑机接口]]的项目，对[[超人文主義|超人文主義]]思想产生了兴趣。于当年参加[[佐治亚理工学院|佐治亚理工学院]]的夏季交流项目，她的研究主题为“神经科学与意识”。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://pwp.gatech.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/516/2016/10/PotterGroup.html |title=People |publisher=[[佐治亚理工学院|Georgia Institute of Technology]] |quote=Alexandra Elbakyan [...] Summer 2010 [...] Programming and data analysis |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170111210530/http://pwp.gatech.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/516/2016/10/PotterGroup.html |archive-date=2017-01-11 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2017-08-07 }}</ref>

她于2011年返回哈萨克斯坦后创建了Sci-Hub，《[[科学_(期刊)|科学]]》称该网站为“可敬的利他主义抑或大型犯罪组织，取决于你是哪方”。<ref name="Bohannon-28-April-2016">{{cite journal|first=John|last=Bohannon|title=The frustrated science student behind Sci-Hub|journal=[[科学_(期刊)|Science]]|doi=10.1126/science.aaf5675|url=http://www.sciencemag.org/news/2016/04/alexandra-elbakyan-founded-sci-hub-thwart-journal-paywalls|date=2016-04-29|volume=352|number=6285|access-date=2017-08-07|archive-date=2017-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170718002509/http://www.sciencemag.org/news/2016/04/alexandra-elbakyan-founded-sci-hub-thwart-journal-paywalls|dead-url=no}}</ref>Sci-Hub对本应付费的学术论文提供提供大量自动且免费的下载。她被出版商[[愛思唯爾|愛思唯爾]]在美国法院起诉，被判赔偿1500万美元罚金。<ref>{{cite news |first=Stephen |last=Buranyi |url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2017/jun/27/profitable-business-scientific-publishing-bad-for-science |title=Is the staggeringly profitable business of scientific publishing bad for science? |newspaper=[[衛報|The Guardian]] |date=2017-06-27 |accessdate=2017-08-07 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927095152/https://www.theguardian.com/science/2017/jun/27/profitable-business-scientific-publishing-bad-for-science |dead-url=no }}</ref>艾爾巴金为了逃避引渡的风险，因此四处躲藏。<ref name="JB">{{cite journal|1=|first=John|last=Bohannon|title=Who's downloading pirated papers? Everyone|journal=[[科学_(期刊)|Science]]|doi=10.1126/science.aaf5664|url=http://www.sciencemag.org/news/2016/04/whos-downloading-pirated-papers-everyone|date=2016-04-29|volume=352|number=6285|pages=508–512|access-date=2017-08-07|archive-date=2019-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513024954/https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2016/04/whos-downloading-pirated-papers-everyone|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年，她获得了硕士学位，并一度被美国机构怀疑为俄国间谍。

2020年，她居住在[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]，和开始在[[俄罗斯科学院|俄罗斯科学院]]哲学研究中心攻读博士学位，专业为知识理论（Theory of Knowledge)<ref>{{Cite web|last=Weinberg|first=Justin|date=2021-07-07|title=Sci-Hub & the Philosophy Grad Student "Pirate Queen"|url=https://dailynous.com/2021/07/07/sci-hub-philosophy-grad-student-pirate-queen/|access-date=2021-11-02|website=Daily Nous|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220113160619/https://dailynous.com/2021/07/07/sci-hub-philosophy-grad-student-pirate-queen/}}</ref>。

== [[Sci-Hub|Sci-Hub]] ==
{{main|Sci-Hub}}

2009 年，在大學攻讀文憑期間，她面臨這樣一個事實，即工作所需的科學期刊上的許多文章都是付費獲取的，這是她負擔不起的。這些文章必須繞過付費訪問系統下載。從 2011 年開始，Elbakyan 開始參與幫助參與者免費下載文章的科學論壇。但是，手動下載文章需要花費大量時間和精力。這促使她利用自己的編程經驗將流程自動化，並創建了Sci-Hub。

她聲稱，她的目標是消除科學知識在社會中的傳播障礙，並為社會縮小數字鴻溝。

